Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
Hello. I would like to see an apartment please.
What is your name/
Could you give me your name, please?
My name is Ben, and I would like to see the Shadyside Apartments Friday at 7:00pm please.
You suddenly remember that you have a friend's wedding on Friday at 7 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
Have you paid the application fee already?
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
I really can not recall if I did not not.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
You will need to pay at the viewing. Is that okay?
You will need to pay at the viewing, is that okay?
Sure. But I forgot my friends wedding is on Friday. I can not do Friday. Sorry.

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
What day would you like?
What day would you like to make the booking for?
We can do Thursday at 7:00 that way I can tell all my friends at the wedding about the new apartment. :)
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your friend's wedding. [instruction 5 of 6]
that time is available
Great, there is still a viewing available at that time. Would you like me to book it for you?
How many bathrooms does it have?
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
It has 2 bathrooms
The apartment has 1.5 baths.
Great. Lets book the viewing please.
